commit.message:
libchafa: Add an AVX2-optimized path for symbol error calculation

This gives an overall speedup of 10-20% over SSE 4.1 with -w 9.

chafa: Detect iTerm image mode

Fixes #196 (GitHub).

chafa: Strip output from "tmux show"

This prevents setting the passthrough option needlessly.

See #195 (GitHub).
ChafaWorkCell: Remove obsolete comment
TODO: Remove done items

chafa: Emit newline/index after sixel image

This positions the cursor correctly ~everywhere.

See #192 (GitHub).

ChafaSixelCanvas: Don't emit GNL after final sixel band

The final GNL could cause extra space to be emitted in some
circumstances.

Also fix an issue causing more bands to be padded than necessary when
multithreaded.

See #192 (GitHub).
ChafaWorkCell: Remove obsolete structs

pixops: Replace shellsort with radix sort

Enabled by the fact that color channels are now guaranteed to be
8-bit. Improves symbol conversion speed by over 20% in my tests.
ci: Remove libjxl-dev dependency again; Jammy doesn't have it

ChafaCanvas: Fix a small memory leak

Fixes #190 (GitHub).
ci: Add dependencies for the JPEG XL loader
tests: Add a test pixel for the JPEG XL loader
vector: Move vector maths into a separate header

Fix Makefile.am for zsh completion

`install-zsh-completion` was only added as a phony target, and running `make install-zsh-completion` does nothing.

Fixes this by declaring the target properly.
README: Add link to JavaScript bindings
jxl: fix indentation and add copyright / author
Only use 4 channels when needed on jxl decoding
Small refracto on jxl loading
Basic implementation of JPEG XL loading using libjxl
tests: Add a test driver that prints fail logs to console
Post-release version bump to 1.15.0
Prepare for 1.14.0 release
chafa: Add missing errno.h include
ChafaPlacement: Improve docs wording
ChafaIterm2Canvas: Enable sRGB handling
pixops: Blend in background color correctly
smolscale: Fix alpha channel being left out on some paths
smolscale: Fix premultiplied+linear paths (use inner premul)
docs: Generate deprecated API index and by version of introduction
